Welcome to the Engineering Joke Generator! This simple web application allows you to lighten up your day with engineering humor. Just type in a keyword related to engineering, such as "computer," "software," or "mechanical," and click the "Generate Joke" button. You'll get a random engineering joke that matches your input. Whether you're an engineer or just looking for a good laugh, this tool is here to bring a smile to your face with engineering-themed jokes. Enjoy the wit and creativity of engineering humor!

